Tokyo Deli serves the finest, freshly prepared authentic sushi and poke available. We bring together the highest quality ingredients from Japan and the finest locally sourced organic ingredients available. Tantalize your senses with our freshly prepared entrees, sushi and poke, and quench your thirst with our signature cocktails. Our menu features a wide variety of fresh, flavorful and affordable lunch and dinner options. We welcome you to dine-in, order on-the-go, or have your meals delivered to your home or office.
